Chordate:



He let out a small sigh as Feline began kissing his neck, and purring 
into his audio receptors.  Reaching the access hatch, he put his hand 
against the scanner, putting in a password.  The door opened, 
Chordate spotting Wolveritron.  "Hey, go on inside.  Situation is 
under control." he said, continuing to walk.
